h trình ấy của Thạch Mục cũng chẳng hề dễ dàng, gian nan và cũng không thiếu nguy hiểm. Từ những trận chiến thập tử nhất sinh, tưởng hẹo mười mươi, cho đến những ngày tháng bị rượt đuổi chạy như bị Tào Tháo rượt, những những khoảnh khắc ấy đã tôi luyện cho Thạch Mục ngày càng trưởng thành, trở thành một võ giả có thể cứu rỗi tương lai của muôn người.","popularity":8.298,"poster_path":"/sTCWzoUUQHT36uS9Kt2O3qXGSoM.jpg","production_companies":[{"id":123270,"logo_path":"/4KxfGr13VXMr44og11hzpdwfQDQ.png","name":"bilibili","origin_country":"CN"},{"id":208526,"logo_path":null,"name":"BYMENT","origin_country":"CN"}],"production_countries":[{"iso_3166_1":"CN","name":"China"}],"seasons":[{"air_date":"2025-11-26","episode_count":26,"id":476705,"name":"Season 1","overview":"","poster_path":"/88eylq2rbHMSv4Do9RoFpj5fuFt.jpg","season_number":1,"vote_average":0}],"spoken_languages":[{"english_name":"Mandarin","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话"}],"status":"Returning Series","tagline":"","type":"Scripted","vote_average":8,"vote_count":1}},"tv_250307_keywords":{"at":1774370505373,"data":{"id":250307,"results":[{"name":"hospital","id":11612},{"name":"pittsburgh, pennsylvania","id":193594},{"name":"medical drama","id":208788},{"name":"medical procedural","id":298849},{"name":"critical","id":315053}]}},"tv_270420_detail_vi-VN":{"at":1774370508119,"data":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/sa9igU1XIER6bMgtZ2Ejfo1KsD8.jpg","created_by":[{"id":125729,"credit_id":"696ce3fc8bf590e26e8fcc70","name":"김정권","original_name":"김정권","gender":2,"profile_path":"/jbPWTA2sJ5QhzJCp985WDIUzYVf.jpg"}],"episode_run_time":[60],"first_air_date":"2026-01-16","genres":[{"id":10765,"name":"Sci-Fi & Fantasy"},{"id":35,"name":"Phim Hài"},{"id":18,"name":"Phim Chính Kịch"}],"homepage":"https://programs.sbs.co.kr/drama/humanfromtoday/main","id":270420,"in_production":false,"languages":["ko"],"last_air_date":"2026-02-28","last_episode_to_air":{"id":5646131,"name":"Episode 12","overview":"","vote_average":0,"vote_count":0,"air_date":"2026-02-28","episode_number":12,"episode_type":"finale","production_code":"","runtime":65,"season_number":1,"show_id":270420,"still_path":"/oYQY1T0M22pIgZNTpyHMfS4vNbm.jpg"},"name":"Từ Hôm Nay, Tôi Là Con Người","next_episode_to_air":null,"networks":[{"id":156,"logo_path":"/uHQFPvRTlpgaIFQVN8eKWEnFOll.png","name":"SBS","origin_country":"KR"}],"number_of_episodes":12,"number_of_seasons":1,"origin_country":["KR"],"original_language":"ko","original_name":"오늘부터 인간입니다만","overview":"Một sinh vật huyền bí đầy phóng túng. Một ngôi sao bóng đá tự mãn. Khi số phận đảo lộn cuộc sống của họ, liệu cả hai có thể thay đổi nhau theo hướng tốt đẹp hơn?","popularity":9.0842,"poster_path":"/wPqwfPOfJOMLFR1ZF2HL6mcpVas.jpg","production_companies":[{"id":144329,"logo_path":"/83KDOfXjQvrCQTqodVauEc5nujJ.png","name":"Binge Works","origin_country":"KR"},{"id":209269,"logo_path":"/A7g3WhW4bu6Y3XBZCQFAXm5G2Mq.png","name":"MOG Films","origin_country":"KR"}],"production_countries":[{"iso_3166_1":"KR","name":"South Korea"}],"seasons":[{"air_date":"2026-01-16","episode_count":12,"id":416562,"name":"Season 1","overview":"","poster_path":"/jkPpdb7WAsomi6Fc68qRiTpTSpl.jpg","season_number":1,"vote_average":7}],"spoken_languages":[{"english_name":"Korean","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말"}],"status":"Ended","tagline":"","type":"Scripted","vote_average":7.7,"vote_count":30}},"person_58050_translations":{"at":1774370515077,"data":{"id":58050,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"反町隆史（日语：反町 隆史／そりまち たかし Sorimachi Takashi，1973年12月19日—），日本男演员，埼玉县出身，本名野口隆史（日语：野口 隆史／のぐち たかし Noguchi Takashi）。\n\n反町出生于埼玉县埼玉市南区。曾经加入杰尼斯事务所，为小杰尼斯“平家派”成员之一。高校时已为时尚模特儿，还曾作为歌手活动。现隶属于研音事务所，血型AB型，身高181公分。其妻为女演员松岛菜菜子。\n\n反町在中学三年级时，以本名“野口隆史”加入杰尼斯事务所，并以平家派的成员之一进行演艺活动及为当红的前辈团体光GENJI担任伴舞。翌年，自身选择离开事务所。之后，在拉面店打工并兼职从事模特儿活动，还曾在巴黎时装周出场。在私下里，会去拳击健身房锻炼体型，并持续写歌词等创作活动。\n\n1994年春天，加入研音事务所，改艺名为现在的名字。名字由来来自于拳击选手龙反町，同时社长希望他能够成为“像龙一样的男人”。同年7月，正式于电视剧《爱情麻辣烫》以演员身份出道。之后，陆续在电视剧活跃着并在1997年以歌手身份开始发行歌曲。\n\n1997年至1998年期间，陆续在《处女之路》、《海滩男孩》、《麻辣教师GTO》等电视剧里担当主演且成绩亮眼开始走红成名。其中，在《麻辣教师GTO》中饰演曾经是暴走族的高中教师“鬼冢英吉”，此剧最终回收视率达到35.7%并创下纪录，受到相当大的瞩目和观众的喜爱。反町也在这些他主演的电视剧里演唱主题曲，例如与竹野内丰共演的海滩男孩的主题曲《Forever》，以及麻辣教师GTO里的主题曲《POISON》。其中以《Forever》一曲登上1997年的第48回NHK红白歌会。\n\n另外，反町也与曾在《麻辣教师GTO》里合作拍摄的松岛菜菜子相恋，并于2001年2月21日，最后一场国内巡回演唱会结束后登记结婚。隔天，反町在官方网站上给媒体及各位粉丝宣布喜讯，并于富士电视台召开记者会。由于两人当时人气当红，瞩目程度颇高，消息一出更是轰动一时，演艺圈又一对明星夫妇诞生了。同年，与刘德华共同主演《全职杀手》，该片并入围第26届多伦多国际电影节。2002年，第一次出演NHK大河剧《利家与松》，并且是与松岛菜菜子结婚后的首次夫妇共演。在该片中饰演织田信长，获得好评并令人印象深刻。其中剧中台词之一，织田信长的口头禅“で、あるか”，还成为当时流行语。\n\n2004年长女出生，2007年次女出生。由于夫妇俩对小孩隐私相当保护，并且把工作与生活区分开，因此从没有让两位女儿曝光过。\n\n2015年10月获邀出演由资深演员水谷丰主演的国民刑事剧《相棒》第14季，剧中饰演从法务省借调到警视厅的精英官员“冠城亘”，成为第四代的“相棒”搭档。之后继续出演第15季、第16季、第17季、第18季、第19季、第20季，直到2022年完成“相棒20”后宣告毕业。\n\n2023年9月，关西电视台、富士电视台宣布为纪念开台65周年，将于2024年春季推出特别篇日剧《麻辣教师GTO Revival》，睽违26年，再次由反町隆史主演。2024年2月，官方剧组公布曾于1998年剧集版中饰演学生的洼冢洋介、小栗旬、池内博之、山崎裕太、德山秀典以及饰演鬼冢的警察好友藤木直人将参演其中。3月26日，官方再公布松岛菜菜子确定会以当年角色身份回归演出，同日释出了由BLUE ENCOUNT加上反町隆史演唱全新编曲的主题曲《POISON》MV。《麻辣教师GTO Revival》于4月1日晚正式播出后引发了网络话题。","name":"反町隆史","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Takashi Sorimachi","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"소리마치 타카시","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"反町隆史","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CZ","iso_639_1":"cs","name":"Český","english_name":"Czech","data":{"biography":"","name":"Takaši Sorimači","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"PL","iso_639_1":"pl","name":"Polski","english_name":"Polish","data":{"biography":"","name":"Takashi Sorimachi","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"Takashi Sorimachi","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"1973 年 12 月 19 日出生於日本埼玉縣埼玉市南區。日本男演員、歌手、模特。\n\n1987 年，加入日本傑尼斯事務所的“平家派”團體；1988 年，退出傑尼斯，開始從事模特工作；1994 年加入研音事務所，改藝名為反町隆史，同年 7 月，透過 透過 透過 通過出演電視劇《愛情麻辣燙》而作為演員出道。1997 年，作為歌手發行了音樂作品還舉辦了演唱會。同年，出演了電視劇《通向婚紗之路》而被觀眾熟知；同年主演電視劇《沙灘男孩》。\n\n1998 年，主演了電視劇《GTO》，該劇最高收視率 35.7%並創下記錄，他也憑該劇獲得第 18 屆日劇學院獎最佳男主角提名。2001 年，與劉德華共同主演了電影《全職殺手》。2015 年，主演電視劇《限界聚落株式會社》和朝日台 SP 劇《迷宮搜查》；同年 10 月，出演的電視劇《相棒第 14 季》播出。2016 年，出演朝日台劇集《相棒第十五季》和《相棒劇場版 4》。2017 年，繼續出演朝日台劇集《相棒第十六季》。","name":"反町隆史","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Такаші Сорімачі","primary":false}}]}},"person_2331360_translations":{"at":1774370521879,"data":{"id":2331360,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"IT","iso_639_1":"it","name":"Italiano","english_name":"Italian","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Melody Hurd is an actress, known for Battle at Big Rock (2019), Them (2021) and Fatherhood (2021).","name":"Melody Hurd","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"美樂蒂·赫德","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Мелоди Хёрд","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"IL","iso_639_1":"he","name":"עִבְרִית","english_name":"Hebrew","data":{"biography":"","name":"מלודי הרד","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"美樂蒂·赫德","primary":false}}]}},"person_2215763_translations":{"at":1774370527462,"data":{"id":2215763,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Percy Daggs IV is the son of Percy Daggs III. He has appeared in several movies and television shows, including The Last Days of Ptolemy Grey, Never Let Go, and Paradise. In 2025, he was nominated for a